export const modalStyle = {
  position: "absolute",
  top: "20%",
  left: "50%",
  transform: "translate(-50%, -50%)",
  width: 400,
  bgcolor: "background.paper",
  border: "1px solid #000",
  p: 4,
  borderRadius: 2,
};
